summary: A new player house, based on the Thalmor Embassy.  A few servants still reside here, mainly doing aimless duties and maintaining the manor.
descriptionHtml:
A new player house, based on the Thalmor Embassy.  A few servants still reside here, mainly doing aimless duties and maintaining the manor.  It is located North of Whiterun jsut at the edge of the mountains.  It has everything a person could want or need.   A library just waiting for all your books.  A weapons room to store all your weapons, including display cases.  Several armour maniquins reside in the main hall.  In the Solar, their is an enchanting table as well as an alchemist table.

This is just the first release fo theis house, as it is my first attempt at doing one.  Any suggestions or tips are appreciated of course.
author: Noctoos
